    • Constructor Detail

      • Post

        public Post​(int id,
            java.util.Date creationDate,
            java.util.Date deletionDate,
            int score,
            java.lang.String body,
            java.util.Date lastEditDate,
            java.util.Date closedDate,
            java.util.Date communityOwnedDate,
            User owner,
            User lastEditor)
        Create a post with all the attributes (null possible)
        Parameters:
        id - The post id
        creationDate - the date when the post has been created
        deletionDate - the date when the post has been deleted, null if the post hasn't been deleted
        score - The post score on SO
        body - The post body
        lastEditDate - The last time the post has been edited
        closedDate - The date when the post has been closed (null if the answer is open)
        communityOwnedDate - The date when the post started to belong to the community
        owner - The user that owns the post
        lastEditor - The last editor of the post
